                        <interp inst="t18401019-2406-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 26.—<rs id="t18401019-2406-punishment-4" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18401019-2406-punishment-4" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2406-18401019 t18401019-2406-punishment-4"></join>Transported for Seven Years.</rs>
               </p>
